集合  出发  吾尚存者
- Company up! Move it out! - It is rather

85
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:06,150
小伙子  该归队了  谢谢你们
Boys, best go and find your company. Thank you.

86
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:08,160
