有一种无形的伟大力量蕴于民众团结之中
that there is a great invisible strength in a people's union?

2029
02:09:20,120 --> 02:09:22,260
即使承受巨大的牺牲
Say we've shown that a people can endure

2030
02:09:22,260 --> 02:09:25,350
我们也做到了团结一致
awful sacrifice and yet cohere?

2031
02:09:26,400 --> 02:09:30,370
这难道还不够挽救人们对民主的信念
Mightn't that save at least the idea of democracy to aspire to?

2032
02:09:31,270 --> 02:09:33,670
并最终让他们觉得民主是值得的吗
Eventually, to become worthy of?

2033
02:09:37,790 --> 02:09:41,170
无论如何  流血和牺牲能证明的东西
At all rates, whatever may be proven by blood and sacrifice

2034
02:09:41,200 --> 02:09:43,600
现在都已经证明
must've been proved by now.

2035
02:09:53,980 --> 02:09:56,390
我们能结束这场血战吗
Shall we stop this bleeding?

2036
02:10:20,580 --> 02:10:26,750
弗吉尼亚州  彼得堡市外  4月3日

2037
02:11:34,800 --> 02:11:38,130
投降之后  把战士们送回他们的家园
Once he surrenders, send his boys back to their homes,

2038
02:11:38,350 --> 02:11:40,610
他们的农场  他们的店铺
their farms, their shops.

2039
02:11:42,140 --> 02:11:45,580
是的  先生  像我们说定的那样
Yes sir, as we discussed.

2040
02:11:45,650 --> 02:11:49,350
宽大处理  不要惩罚  我不想那样
Liberality all around. No punishment. I don't want that.

2041
02:11:50,010 --> 02:11:52,670
领头的那些  杰夫跟其他人
And the leaders, Jeff and the rest of 'em.

2042
02:11:52,800 --> 02:11:54,930
就算他们趁我不留意逃到国外
If they escape, leave the country while my back's turned,

2043
02:11:54,930 --> 02:11:56,980
我也不会追究
that wouldn't upset me none.

2044
02:11:57,990 --> 02:12:00,750
和平不是表面工作
When peace comes it mustn't just be hangings.

2045
02:12:07,170 --> 02:12:09,070
看看你的外表
By outward appearance,

2046
02:12:10,440 --> 02:12:12,990
比去年老了十岁
you're ten years older than you were a year ago.

2047
02:12:16,610 --> 02:12:19,490
疲倦已经深入骨髓了
Some weariness has bit at my bones.

2048
02:12:32,220 --> 02:12:36,230
我从未想过一切会是今天看到的这样
I never seen the like of it before. What I seen today.

2049
02:12:38,190 --> 02:12:40,590
从未想过
Never seen the like of it before.

2050
02:12:42,440 --> 02:12:46,940
你一直都知道  你知道会是这样
You always knew that what this was going to be.

2051
02:12:48,570 --> 02:12:50,970
尸体挨着尸体  面目全非
Intimate, and ugly.

2052
02:12:53,960 --> 02:12:55,270
当你决定来这里的时候
You must've needed to see it close

2053
02:12:55,280 --> 02:12:57,590
一定是想近距离看一看吧
when you decided to come down here.

2054
02:13:16,340 --> 02:13:19,700
我们给了彼此机会去做可怕的事情
We've made it possible for one another to do terrible things.

2055
02:13:22,460 --> 02:13:24,450
并且赢了这场战争
And we've won the war.

2056
02:13:24,930 --> 02:13:28,300
现在你必须带领我们走出它的阴影
Now you have to lead us out of it.

2057
02:13:39,360 --> 02:13:45,530
阿波马托克斯郡府  弗吉尼亚州  1865年4月9日

2058
02:15:00,140 --> 02:15:01,880
想去旅行吗
You've an itch to travel?

2059
02:15:03,320 --> 02:15:04,880
挺想的
I'd like that.

2060
02:15:05,480 --> 02:15:07,540
坐火车去西部
To the West by rail.

2061
02:15:07,820 --> 02:15:10,220
我说的去国外
Overseas.

2062
02:15:11,410 --> 02:15:12,970
去基督圣地[指巴勒斯坦]
The Holy Land.

2063
02:15:15,760 --> 02:15:17,440
跟妻子在耶稣受难日
Awfully pious for a man

2064
02:15:17,440 --> 02:15:20,350
坐马车出来兜风  你可真虔诚
who takes his wife out buggy-riding on Good Friday.

2065
02:15:20,570 --> 02:15:22,140
去耶路撒冷
Jerusalem.

2066
02:15:22,290 --> 02:15:24,400
大卫跟所罗门走过的地方
Where David and Solomon walked.

2067
02:15:24,580 --> 02:15:28,340
我做梦都想踏上那座古城
I dream of walking in that ancient city.

2068
02:15:34,120 --> 02:15:35,770
所有人都会认为我是个疯子
All anyone will remember of me is

2069
02:15:35,770 --> 02:15:38,580
我毁了你的幸福
I was crazy and I ruined your happiness.

2070
02:15:39,380 --> 02:15:42,650
这样想的人都不了解  玛丽
Anyone thinks that doesn't understand, Mary.

2071
02:15:45,730 --> 02:15:50,300
当人们看着你的时候  他们会想
When they look at you, at what it cost

2072
02:15:50,300 --> 02:15:53,940
付出怎样的代价才能得到他拥有的一切
to live at the heart of this, they'll wonder at it.

2073
02:15:53,940 --> 02:15:56,280
他们会琢磨  这很正常
They'll wonder at you, they should.

2074
02:15:58,120 --> 02:16:00,920
但如果他们真的想知道个中滋味
But they should also look at the wretched woman by your side,

2075
02:16:00,930 --> 02:16:03,340
他们应该来看看你身旁这个可怜的女人
if they want to understand what this was truly like.

2076
02:16:05,020 --> 02:16:09,050
为了普通百姓  为了你之外的其他人
For the ordinary person. For anyone other than you.

2077
02:16:09,110 --> 02:16:11,110
我们要试着高兴起来
We must try to be happier.

2078
02:16:11,670 --> 02:16:13,710
两人都要高兴起来
We must. Both of us.

2079
02:16:14,050 --> 02:16:16,450
我们已经痛苦了太久了
We've been so miserable for so long.

2080
02:16:25,590 --> 02:16:27,990
我确实说过批准某些有色人种
I did say some colored men,

2081
02:16:28,210 --> 02:16:32,900
那些聪明的  受过教育的  打过仗的
the intelligent, the educated, and veterans, i qualified it.

2082
02:16:33,130 --> 02:16:34,050
史蒂文斯先生很愤怒
Mr. Stevens is furious.

2083
02:16:34,050 --> 02:16:36,460
他想知道你为什么会批准
He wants to know why you qualified it.

2084
02:16:36,540 --> 02:16:38,940
没人听说过什么聪明的  受过教育的
No one's heard the intelligent or the educated part.

2085
02:16:38,980 --> 02:16:40,430
他们听到的仅仅是
All they heard was the first time

2086
02:16:40,430 --> 02:16:43,460
历史上第一次有位总统提到了
any president has ever made mention

2087
02:16:43,730 --> 02:16:45,290
黑人选举权
of Negro voting.

2088
02:16:45,540 --> 02:16:49,210
我要是能说的更精彩一点就好了
Still, I wish I had mentioned it in a better speech.

2089
02:16:49,250 --> 02:16:50,450
史蒂文斯先生也想知道
Mr. Stevens also wants to know

2090
02:16:50,460 --> 02:16:52,870
您为什么没有说的更精彩一点
why you didn't make a better speech.

2091
02:16:56,010 --> 02:16:57,820
林肯夫人在马车上等您
Mrs. Lincoln's waiting in the carriage.

2092
02:16:57,880 --> 02:16:59,470
她让我提醒您注意时间  您还要去接
She wants me to remind you of the hour,  and that

2093
02:16:59,480 --> 02:17:02,330
哈里斯小姐跟雷斯本上校
you'll have to pick up Miss Harris and Major Rathbone.

2094
02:17:06,250 --> 02:17:08,140
我有麻烦了吗  没有  先生
- Am I in trouble? - No, sir.

2095
02:17:08,340 --> 02:17:10,140
谢谢你  斯莱德先生
Thank you, Mr. Slade.

2096
02:17:25,380 --> 02:17:27,780
看样子我得走了
I suppose it's time to go,

2097
02:17:28,310 --> 02:17:29,870
虽然我更想留下
though I would rather stay.

2098
02:18:59,950 --> 02:19:02,430
总统被枪杀了
The President has been shot!

2099
02:19:05,510 --> 02:19:09,190
总统在福特剧院被枪杀了
The President has been shot at Ford's Theater!

2100
02:19:51,110 --> 02:19:54,410
现在是  4月15日  周六
It's 7:22 in the morning,

2101
02:19:55,480 --> 02:19:58,430
早上7点22分  一切都结束了
Saturday the 15th of April. It's all over.

2102
02:19:58,640 --> 02:20:01,050
总统离开了人世
The President is no more.

2103
02:20:03,720 --> 02:20:06,120
他已经归于历史长河
Now he belongs to the ages.

2104
02:20:12,300 --> 02:20:17,640
我们温柔期待  我们热忱祈祷(1865年林肯第二次就职演讲)
Fondly do we hope, fervently do we pray,

2105
02:20:19,110 --> 02:20:24,420
但愿这名为战争的灾祸可即刻消逝
that this mighty scourge of war may speedily pass away.

2106
02:20:27,260 --> 02:20:29,660
然而  如果上帝要延续这苦难
Yet, if God wills that it continue

2107
02:20:30,380 --> 02:20:34,050
直到奴役之人数百年来
until all the wealth piled by the bondman's

2108
02:20:34,070 --> 02:20:39,040
以血汗堆积的财富化为乌有
two hundred and fifty years of unrequited toil shall be sunk,

2109
02:20:40,380 --> 02:20:44,250
直到  如数千年前之人所讲
and until every drop of blood drawn with the lash

2110
02:20:44,360 --> 02:20:48,470
鞭打出的血必得以刀刺出的血来偿还
shall be paid by another drawn with the sword,

2111
02:20:49,480 --> 02:20:54,500
直到那时  我们仍旧低吟
as was said three thousand years ago, so still it must be said

2112
02:20:55,000 --> 02:21:03,000
主之审判确是真实且公正的
The judgments of the Lord are true and righteous altogether.

2113
02:21:07,800 --> 02:21:09,830
我们全无恶意
With malice toward none,

2114
02:21:11,940 --> 02:21:14,340
对所有人心怀仁爱
with charity for all,

2115
02:21:15,480 --> 02:21:19,460
我们坚持正义  因上帝以正义启迪我们
with firmness in the right as God gives us to see the right,

2116
02:21:19,490 --> 02:21:22,780
且让我们完成这未竟的事业
let us strive on to finish the work we are in,

2117
02:21:23,580 --> 02:21:25,980
平复这国家的创伤
to bind up the nation's wounds,

2118
02:21:27,040 --> 02:21:31,620
慰藉那些战争中逝去的英灵
to care for him who shall have borne the battle,

2119
02:21:33,640 --> 02:21:36,040
照顾烈士的遗孀及孤儿
and for his widow and his orphan,

2120
02:21:37,780 --> 02:21:42,330
尽一切努力
to do all which may achieve

2121
02:21:43,090 --> 02:21:48,420
以求在本国及世界范围内
and cherish a just and a lasting peace

2122
02:21:49,080 --> 02:21:51,750
保障公平正义及世代和平
among ourselves and with all nations.


